text: Moosach is a town in Upper Bavaria, Germany. Moosach may also refer to several other places or rivers in Germany: * Moosach (Munich), a neighbourhood of the city of Munich * Munich Moosach station, a station on the Munich S-Bahn also leading to the Munich U-Bahn and the tramway network * Moosach (river), a tributary of the Isar
title: Moosach (disambiguation)
